    • startServer

      public int startServer(String ip, int port, boolean isDynamicPort)
      Deprecated.
      Starts the proxy server.

      If the proxy server was already running it's stopped first.

      Parameters:
      ip - the IP/address the server should bind to
      port - the port
      isDynamicPort - true if it should use another port if the given one is already in use, false otherwise.
      Returns:
      the port the server is listening to, or -1 if not able to start
